{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"cbf32200b4","title":"接见国民党驻延安联络参课陈宏递郭卫生和周励武时的谈话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"dd3dd509a0","index":0,"year":1942,"month":9,"day":1,"articleId":"cbf32200b4"}],"tags":[{"id":"314ad57c4d","name":"对话","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji17","name":"毛泽东全集第17卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji17.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji17":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"9cb805222f","type":"paragraph","text":"接见国民党驻延安联络参课陈宏递","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji17","articleId":"cbf32200b4"},{"id":"8bea2e2efd","type":"paragraph","text":"郭卫生和周励武时的谈话！","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji17","articleId":"cbf32200b4"},{"id":"c8980302ae","type":"paragraph","text":"（1942年9月1日）（一）彼方释放叶挺，我方派童必武一人出席参政会，否则仍不能出席：（二）我方决不推翻国民政府，决不越过现有细界，彼方承认我方在敌后有发展权利，承认现有防地，承认边区，在敌后的国共两军，双方下令互不攻击：（三）恢复新四军，发给欠的，停止速捕：（四）何（即何应钦）停止反共，我停止反何，并可重新来往但何若再反共，我必再反何[1]这是毛泽东接见国民党驻延安联络参谋陈宏送、郭卫生和周励武时","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji17","articleId":"cbf32200b4"}],"page":{"id":"ac18f85e99","publicationId":"maoquanji17","articleId":"cbf32200b4","start":134,"end":134}}}},"__N_SSG":true}